{"article_id":"JOilLW83J2qT47fr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"As Republicans scramble to tamp down fears","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that their health care bill would gut protections for sick people ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"they 're running into a chorus of opposition","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"-- from fellow Republicans .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"With direct orders from President Donald Trump","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"to fulfill the GOP 's years-long promise","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to repeal Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"House Republican leaders are trying yet again to get the 216 votes","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"they need","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to pass a bill this week .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Thus far , they 're failing .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"The biggest problem :","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"The legislation would let insurers charge people with pre-existing conditions more for their health care","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"if those people let their insurance lapse at any point .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"It 's an ironic twist in the Republican Party 's crusade","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to gut the Affordable Care Act , the landmark health care law","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"enacted by former President Barack Obama in 2010 .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"A major pillar of the law is the ban on insurance companies from discriminating against people","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"based on their past medical conditions .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Now , even some of the very Republicans","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"who have long vowed to dismantle Obamacare","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"acknowledge","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that that protection is simply untouchable .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"`` From day one , I 've supported the rights of those with pre-existing illnesses","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"to be covered ,","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"and in my view this undermines that effort ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"and I ca n't be a part of it , ''","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"GOP Rep. Fred Upton of Michigan told reporters Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"`` Yes , there are ways","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"to fix it .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"But the proposal","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"that 's on the table now","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"does n't work . ''","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Upton , the former chairman of the House 's Energy and Commerce Committee , will oppose the bill , a significant blow to the GOP leadership .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"He and Rep. Billy Long of Missouri plan to meet at the White House Wednesday morning in hopes","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that an amendment on pre-existing conditions could be negotiated .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Even Republicans","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"who say","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"they are inclined to support the latest House proposal","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"are haunted by the concerns","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"raised by constituents with medical histories .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"In a strikingly candid and extended conversation with reporters in the ornate House Speaker 's Lobby Tuesday afternoon , Rep. Tom Rooney of Florida said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"he has confronted `` extremely angry '' and `` sincerely scared '' constituents back home .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"the most sincere anger","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"I 've noticed","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"comes from people","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"that are sincerely scared ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"people","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"that may have a pre-existing condition","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"that feel like","depth":17},{"id":52,"text":"they 're about to lose it","depth":17},{"id":53,"text":"and they 're going to die ,","depth":16},{"id":54,"text":"and they 're going to die","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"because of a vote","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"that we might be taking , ''","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"Rooney said .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"`` And if we can not explain to people","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that that is not going to happen ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"then it is going to be very difficult to ever bring a bill to the floor , ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"added Rooney ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"he is leaning towards voting for the bill .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"`` Pre-existing conditions are in the bill .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"And I mandate it .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"I said ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"'Has to be , ' ''","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Trump said on CBS 's `` Face the Nation '' Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"In another interview with Bloomberg News , Trump went as far as to claim","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"that the GOP legislation `` will be every bit as good on pre-existing conditions as Obamacare . ''","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"The concern over pre-existing conditions has been so pervasive","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"that CNN 's whip count has 22 House Republicans","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"who have publicly said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"they would vote against the health care bill .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"If 23 Republicans defect ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"the bill would likely fail a floor vote .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Democratic supporters of Obamacare say","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"the GOP 's struggle","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"to repeal it","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"validates the law 's merits .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"`` The injustice","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"of how people with pre-existing conditions had been treated before the Affordable Care Act","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"was its biggest selling point .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"It 's a concern","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"that cuts across lines of race , class and geography , ''","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"said David Axelrod , Obama 's former senior adviser and a CNN contributor .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"`` By tampering with this fundamental element of the law ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"the Republican leadership and White House have touched the third rail of health care politics , ''","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"The hard-to-swallow reality for Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Axelrod said ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"is this :","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"`` It 's very hard to dismantle the ACA","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"and preserve its protections for people with pre-existing conditions . ''","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Republican leadership is engaged in a frenzied whip effort ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"talking with members","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"and educating them in hopes","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"they can get rank-and-filers comfortable with the protections","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"that do exist in the bill for people with pre-existing conditions .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence was on Capitol Hill Monday and Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"talking with Republicans about their concerns ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"and lawmakers have also been speaking with Health and Human Services Secretary Tom Price .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"For decades prior to the enactment of the Affordable Care Act , many Americans were unable to even afford or obtain insurance","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"because of their past medical history .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"As Obamacare has shifted that norm ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Republicans have grown increasingly careful in recent years to say","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"they would not repeal protections for people with pre-existing conditions ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"wary of being branded the party","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"that wants to take that protection away .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"While Republicans have campaigned aggressively to dismantle Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"there has been a quiet recognition","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that gutting protections for people with pre-existing conditions might be a political bridge too far .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Even in the GOP 's 2015 repeal bill","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that was ultimately vetoed by Obama ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Republicans did n't try to repeal the protections .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"That bill was mostly a message effort , however ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"as Obama 's veto was guaranteed .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"This spring , Republicans have majorities in both the House and Senate , and a President","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"excited to repeal Obamacare .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"`` Before 2014 it was all theoretical ,","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"but now it is actual people , ''","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"said Rep. Larry Levitt , a health care policy expert at the Kaiser Family Foundation .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"`` As a kid , I was adamant","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"that I did n't like broccoli","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"no matter how good it was for me","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"but , as an adult , I eat it all the time , ''","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"said Jesse Ferguson , a former Hillary Clinton aide","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"now working with Democrats","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"to oppose Obamacare repeal .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"`` After spending years adamant about repealing health care ,","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"part of the GOP seems to be growing up , ready to eat their broccoli","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"and stop repealing the law","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"because it 's good for us . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":267,"left":0,"right":266,"relat